name: Flymasters
desc: Flymasters helps students find the best colleges and courses for their master's journey. The site offers access to over 800 universities and more than 80,321 courses worldwide, along with visa assistance and guidance. It aims to simplify the process of studying abroad, offering support in over 27 countries and ensuring a successful application with their extensive resources and expertise.
